Lincoln Plumer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lincoln_Plumer 0 Lincoln Plumer (28 September 1875, Maryland - 14 February 1928, Hollywood, California) was an American silent film actor. He married fellow actor Rose Plumer. Lincoln Plumer died of heart disease in 1928.
